  "title": "Technical Assistant (F&B) X 20 @ Tuas | 5 days a week | Shift | up $2500 + allowance",
  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>📍 Location: </strong>Jalan Ahmad Ibrahim</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are ramping up operations for a brand-new Central Kitchen – and we’re looking for 20 dedicated Assistant Technicians to join the team! If you're passionate about food production and have technical hands-on experience, we want you!</p>\n<h3>💼 <strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Set up and operate meal packing lines</li>\n  <li>Troubleshoot packing line issues and improve efficiency</li>\n  <li>Maintain, repair, and ensure safe operation of kitchen and packing equipment</li>\n  <li>Support ad-hoc duties assigned by supervisors</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>📋 <strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Min 2 years' experience in food production/processing/line operations</li>\n  <li>Strong understanding of food processing and packing machinery</li>\n  <li>Hands-on skills in mechanical, electrical, or electronic repairs</li>\n  <li>Physically fit and able to handle labor-intensive, high-volume operations</li>\n  <li>Able to be flexible on shift</li>\n  <li>Food &amp; Hygiene Certificate</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>⏰ <strong>Working Hours &amp; Shifts</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Per day work shift: 9.5 hours (8.75 hrs work + 45-min break)</li>\n  <li>5 working days/week (based on roster, Mon to Sunday)</li>\n  <li>Shift Allowance: Morning shift - additional <em>$8 per day, Noon shift - additional $8 per day, Night shift - additional $15 per day</em></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>💰 <strong>Salary &amp; Benefits</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Base Salary: $2,000 – $2,500 (depending on experience)</li>\n  <li>Allowance as per according to shift roster</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have a strong technical background in food production and thrive in a fast-paced environment, <strong>apply now!</strong><br>\n📧 <strong>Email:</strong> deborah@crew.sg</p>\n<p><br>\n(Please include your resume and availability)</p>\n<p><strong>Ho Yu Qing Deborah (R1104551)</strong><br>\nHRnet Ventures Pte Ltd | EA Licence: <strong>24C2435</strong></p>",
